{"tid":1891164,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[突發, 我地就快輸] YOUTUBE 算法講解 對準政略去打","createTime":"2020-02-21T15:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T04:21:55.000Z","uid":41245,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e914aeb2bf48d5c51529a57a228b4471f44a419","tid":1891164,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"yelol1000000出咗篇長文講解YouTube嘅算法<br />\n大家依家玩CLS，comment like share同subscribe，其實方向啱，但如果要再準確啲打中算法紅心，跟據YouTube工程師自己寫嘅研究報告，其實有7個元素：<br />\n1. Click-through rate（點擊次數）<br />\n2. Watch time（觀看時數）<br />\n3. How many videos the user has watched from your channel（觀眾睇過你幾多條片）<br />\n4. How recently the user watched a video about this topic（有幾近期觀眾睇過依類TOPIC） <br />\n5. What the user has searched for in the past（觀眾SEARCH過）<br />\n6. The user&rsquo;s previously watched videos（觀眾睇過依條片）<br />\n7. The user&rsquo;s demographic information and location（觀眾本身嘅資料同地點）<br />\n<br />\nCLS subscribe其實未係打得中晒全部，仲有幾方面係要做先可以最有效推到條片<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全文：</span><br />\n科學教育CHANNEL Veritasium分析經歷同發展計劃<br />\n+GOOGLE工程師研究報告<br />\n+大J本地情況分析<br />\n1. YOUTUBE回塘現象 <a href=\"https://t.me/YelOL1000000/42\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYelOL1000000%2F42&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=8d38b113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YelOL1000000/42</a><br />\n2. 算法注重嘅嘢 <a href=\"https://t.me/YelOL1000000/43\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYelOL1000000%2F43&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=02609e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YelOL1000000/43</a><br />\n3. [海量j圖] 正妹用胸部夾出標題黨 <a href=\"https://t.me/YelOL1000000/44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYelOL1000000%2F44&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=180a5ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YelOL1000000/44</a><br />\n4. 點喺YOUTUBE到玩 <a href=\"https://t.me/YelOL1000000/45\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYelOL1000000%2F45&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=975270e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YelOL1000000/45</a><br />\n5. 本TG CHANNEL發展方向 <a href=\"https://t.me/YelOL1000000/50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYelOL1000000%2F50&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=ccc8f085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YelOL1000000/50</a>"},{"pid":"33781b02150b6c1db973dfd00dc6575cadfe23e6","tid":1891164,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099de90aee9fd5b05eaec7727ebbd97574f5ef99","tid":1891164,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"大家咁積極係utube 打kol100,咁facebook呢?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891146</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6183b44f9a07b221dfffd7d4e3e0bbe7c37c2a7d","tid":1891164,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c5f3d70371f27568245d9ba79b76d8edafef090","tid":1891164,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"099de90aee9fd5b05eaec7727ebbd97574f5ef99","tid":1891164,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"大家咁積極係utube 打kol100,咁facebook呢?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891146</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"Facebook其實係難打少少<br />\nFacebook啲kol憤然放棄Facebook，就係因為之前Facebook成日改算法又亂又難